{{h1}}Feature Flags

{{h2}}Commands
- `{{#command}}flags/list{{/command}}` - List all flags (project and feature)
- `{{#command}}flags/project/list{{/command}}` - List project flags only
- `{{#command}}flags/feature/list{{/command}}` - List feature flags only

{{h2}}Project Flags
Flags specific to the current project.

Commands:
- `{{#command}}flags/project/get{{/command}} <flag-name>` - Get flag value
- `{{#command}}flags/project/set{{/command}} <flag-name>` - Set flag value
- `{{#command}}flags/project/remove{{/command}} <flag-name>` - Remove flag override

{{h2}}Feature Flags
Flags that apply across all projects.

Commands:
- `{{#command}}flags/feature/get{{/command}} <flag-name>` - Get flag value
- `{{#command}}flags/feature/set{{/command}} <flag-name>` - Set flag value
- `{{#command}}flags/feature/remove{{/command}} <flag-name>` - Remove flag

{{h2}}Available Flags

{{h3}}workflow
Enable workflow phase tracking
- Scope: Project and Feature

{{h3}}openspec
Enable OpenSpec integration
- Scope: Project and Feature

{{h3}}content-style
Output format (None, plain, mime)
- Scope: Project and Feature

{{h3}}autoupdate
Automatic content updates
- Scope: Feature only
